Which three are valid declarations of a float?
 1. float f1 = -343; 
 2. float f2 = 3.14; 
 3. float f3 = 0x12345; 
 4. float f4 = 42e7; 
 5. float f5 = 2001.0D; 
 6. float f6 = 2.81F;

What will be the output of the program? 
 for (int i = 0; i < 4; i += 2) 
 { 
     System.out.print(i + " "); 
  } 
 System.out.println(i); /* Line 5 */
